{"tid":1584127,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(推)罷買無用!!","createTime":"2019-09-21T03:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T03:40:52.000Z","uid":273188,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f54fc37fca87a3af94870e234277d30aafc9b2","tid":1584127,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"事實上 ，現在罷買根本無人覺得係一個抗爭活動，因為全香港的銷售額跌，會覺得銷售跌係因為小左自由行。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現在，所推的罷買無針對性，罷買必須有針對性。<br />\n罷買活動效果必須令大眾看見到，係因為抗爭運動，所以銷售下跌。</span></span><br />\n1. 罷買<br />\n要罷買所有黨鐡商場，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要罷買成功必須令人看到同一個地區相鄰的商場，黨鐡商場是無人去，而其它的商場就好多人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 罷去一整區銷費<br />\n例如，以下2個情況，於今個星期發生在那一個區，下星期在那一個區罷買:<br />\na. 那一個區是出動過防暴警察的話。<br />\nb. 那一個區出現過黑社會打示威者的時候。<br />\n現在最好係罷買北角。<br />\n即使你住在那一個區，放左工去食飯都唔好返自己果一區食飯。<br />\n現在，最好係罷買北角，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要比人睇到,在那一區的商鋪係比其它區小人行街。</span></span><br />\n如果，你想去買電器，都請你去其它區的店鋪買。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵商場 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;替代商場</span></span>)<br />\n圓方<br />\n德福廣場(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;淘大花園/商場</span></span>)<br />\n青衣城  (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;青怡廣場</span></span>)<br />\nPopCorn (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n綠楊坊 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;荃灣千色滙</span></span>)<br />\nCitylink 連城廣場(<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;沙田中心</span></span>)<br />\n杏花新城<br />\n連理街 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n海趣坊 (<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;啟豐商場</span></span></span>)<br />\n駿景廣場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;銀禧花園</span></span></span>)<br />\n新屯門商場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;富健花園</span></span>)<br />\n恒福商場 (<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改去---&gt;置樂商場</span></span>)<br />\nThe lohas(<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改去---&gt;將軍澳廣場</span></span>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/shops/more_malls.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fshops%2Fmore_malls.html&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd77KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=e28b37bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/shops/more_malls.html</a>"},{"pid":"65770761e1dd73a40a8c9ff55ba4de0a3dee2e00","tid":1584127,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"6eb52beacdc4beabc928a669bad0c2b2d970d666","tid":1584127,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"大埔呢。。。。。？？<br />\n大埔超級城好似都係Sell H.K...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2047167a2ef17476e84160a85e6e79b028b08465","tid":1584127,"uid":54629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6eb52beacdc4beabc928a669bad0c2b2d970d666","tid":1584127,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"大埔呢。。。。。？？<br />\n大埔超級城好似都係Sell H.K...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"去其他區算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br